== 反应试剂的制备 ==
Corey–Chaykovsky试剂和二甲基亚甲基硫叶立德可分别通过[[二甲基亚砜|二甲基亚砜]]和[[二甲基硫醚|二甲基硫醚]]与[[碘甲烷|碘甲烷]]形成[[鎓盐|鎓盐]]，然后用强碱（如[[氢化钠|氢化钠]]<ref>{{cite journal|author=Corey, E. J.; Chaykovsky, M.|journal=[[有机合成_(期刊)|Organic Syntheses]]|year=1969|volume=49|pages=78|url=http://www.orgsyn.org/orgsyn/prep.asp?prep=cv5p0755|title=METHYLENECYCLOHEXANE OXIDE|access-date=2009-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100331041814/http://www.orgsyn.org/orgsyn/prep.asp?prep=cv5p0755|archive-date=2010-03-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 或[[正丁基锂|正丁基锂]]）去质子化形成。Corey–Chaykovsky试剂不稳定，一般在反应中原位制备并进行反应。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Dimethylsulfoxonium Methylide|author=E. J. Corey, Michael Chaykovsky|journal=J. Am. Chem. Soc.|year=1962|volume=84|issue=5|pages=867–868|doi=10.1021/ja00864a040}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Dimethyloxosulfonium Methylide ((CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>SOCH<sub>2</sub>) and Dimethylsulfonium Methylide ((CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>SCH<sub>2</sub>). Formation and Application to Organic Synthesis|author=E. J. Corey, Michael Chaykovsky|journal=J. Am. Chem. Soc.|year=1965|volume=87|issue=6|pages=1353–1364|doi=10.1021/ja01084a034}}</ref>

